title: Ocean Minded™ Croslite™ Collection
description:
Many or our Ocean Minded™ footwear styles feature Croslite™ material -- a proprietary, revolutionary technology that gives each pair the soft, comfortable, lightweight and odor-resistant qualities our customers have come to love and expect.

Additionally, Croslite™ material is non-marking, easy to clean, and forms to your foot for all-day comfort, providing us with a key point of differentiation in the marketplace.
